## ðŸ”§ How to Run Database

Import the project into your NetBeans.
Set up the Derby database by inserting the lostfoundsystem folder into this path "C:\Users<Username>\AppData\Roaming\NetBeans\Derby".
Clean & Build and run the project.
Access the application via http://localhost:8080/LostFoundSystem_03/ in your browser.

-----OR-----

CREATE NEW DATABASE
## ðŸ”§ HOW TO CREATE NEW DATABASE ?

1. Buka tab `Services` di NetBeans
2. Right-click `Java DB` > `Create Database`
   - Database Name: lostfoundsystem
   - Username: app
   - Password: app
3. Right-click `lostfoundsystem` > `Execute Command`
4. Copy & paste dari line 22 - 65
5. Tekan F6 untuk run semua command

CREATE TABLE USERS (
ID INT PRIMARY KEY GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY,
FULLNAME VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
EMAIL VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
PASSWORD VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE LOST_ITEMS (
ID INT PRIMARY KEY GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY,
USER_ID INT,
ITEM_NAME VARCHAR(100),
CATEGORY VARCHAR(50),
DESCRIPTION VARCHAR(255),
DATE_LOST DATE,
LOCATION_LOST VARCHAR(300), 
CONTACT_INFO VARCHAR(255),
TRACKING_NUMBER VARCHAR(50),
COURIER_SERVICE VARCHAR(100),
PARCEL_STATUS VARCHAR(50), 
FOREIGN KEY (USER_ID) REFERENCES USERS(ID)
);

CREATE TABLE FOUND_ITEMS (
ID INT PRIMARY KEY GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY,
USER_ID INT,
ITEM_NAME VARCHAR(100),
CATEGORY VARCHAR(50),
DESCRIPTION VARCHAR(255),
DATE_FOUND DATE,
LOCATION_FOUND VARCHAR(300), 
CONTACT_INFO VARCHAR(255),
TRACKING_NUMBER VARCHAR(50),
COURIER_SERVICE VARCHAR(100),
PARCEL_STATUS VARCHAR(50),  
FOREIGN KEY (USER_ID) REFERENCES USERS(ID)
);

CREATE TABLE FEEDBACK (
ID INT PRIMARY KEY GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY,
USER_ID INT,
CUSTOMER_NAME VARCHAR(100),
EMAIL VARCHAR(100),
RATING INT,           
COMMENTS VARCHAR(500),
